name: VoIP ID Book Project
tagline: Book writing project, a manual or user and admin guide, for VoIP ID
body:
VoIP ID is a Free and Open Source Software to build a hosted VoIP server or hosted IPPBX service. Please visit [VoIP ID project](http://antonraharja.github.io/voip-id) for more information.

# Table of Contents

* English version of the book are available [book-contents](https://github.com/antonraharja/book-voip-id/blob/master/book-contents/en/README.md) folder.
* Other related documents are available in [documents](https://github.com/antonraharja/book-voip-id/blob/master/documents/README.md) folder.
